{"tid":1468583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【推上國際】英國外相表示關注機場衝突丶同場加映trump證實大量解放軍抵達香港邊境","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:36:08.000Z","uid":219244,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"22af7bc13ea518ec96b0eeaa8e187395db91f22d","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:48.000Z","msg":"有國際關注係好事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ4YROO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ4YROO.png&h=d553df37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知前線手足好燥底，尤其好嬲811<br />\n但都請你地凡事<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">保持冷靜</span></strong><br />\n就算俾你打死一丶兩隻狗都救唔番女義士隻眼<br />\n只有獨立調查委員會先可以搵返開槍條仆街，告到佢坐監！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住我地應該係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標導向</strong></span>，啫係每個action都係purpose for<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong>，而<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>唔係情緒主導</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打完可能你地出咗啖氣，但係被捕兄弟呢？<br />\n只有五大訴求先可以救翻佢哋出嚟啊，所以記得做每個行動之前都諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日美國暫緩部份中國貨品關稅，應該係貿易戰利好好消息<br />\n但同時trump確認有大量解放軍扺達香港邊境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZ68uzR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZ68uzR.png&h=18dbc644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想知聽日恆指會升定跌<br />\n究竟對於香港股市嚟講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中美貿易戰</strong></span>重要啲定係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港前途</strong></span>重要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c406eaad7db68c47ce8a93a3b334bd1741c3c953","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:44.000Z","msg":"大家覺得聽日究竟股市升定跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49b4e71584e4b7925db132ad0ca4dab56779500","tid":1468583,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:21:39.000Z","msg":"ppp"},{"pid":"04389417ac0319cf899303491b7a61b761e892a9","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"記住我地應該係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標導向</span></span></strong>，啫係每個action都係purpose for五大訴求，而<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>唔係情緒主導</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>打完可能你地出咗啖氣，但係被捕兄弟呢</strong></span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></strong>先可以救翻佢哋出嚟啊，所以記得做每個行動之前都諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc6d875ecafdbfb1fdaaba20d6ad50d1d4c134f","tid":1468583,"uid":35364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"d5e2650679286c08e0c700df89c7b595c6617230","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:40.000Z","msg":"仲有侵侵咁提水啫係佢confirm有軍事介入風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前成日都睇死中共唔敢派解放軍<br />\n係咪依家要開始討論一下如果解放軍入城要點做<br />\n就算最後唔派，討論下都冇死<br />\n有準備好過冇準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講一句<br />\n連登仔唔好以為中共一定唔會派軍隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要知道係中共眼中維持統治&gt;經濟<br />\n雖則話係焦土，但都要諗下旦軍隊入城要點做"},{"pid":"2b49834223001656da3123befe57b08915fb4d50","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqWcWin.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqWcWin.gif&h=ea589ede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e99cecc56fe72639b92c2d6664a53f1f81e8a229","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:28:46.000Z","msg":"聽日會唔會股災<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定係大陸股一於少理香港，受惠於中美貿易戰緩和而推高大市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb656c00255f52fcc6ab9e2b0a928e301cc082e","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:30:56.000Z","msg":"關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發 凌晨4點柒婆見記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468411</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ea4196d4a35dc2971f2b0f19e2e5141561d3664","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04389417ac0319cf899303491b7a61b761e892a9","tid":1468583,"uid":219244,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"記住我地應該係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標導向</span></span></strong>，啫係每個action都係purpose for五大訴求，而<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>唔係情緒主導</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"col